  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/d96676e898b812dce13ac7a778d2fef5.poster.avif?t=1750256150\" width=596 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/d96676e898b812dce13ac7a778d2fef5.webm?t=1750256150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/d96676e898b812dce13ac7a778d2fef5.mp4?t=1750256150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/c1aa74e650c607a10c3ff15ffc4ed14e.avif?t=1750256150\" width=350 height=150 /></span><br>Kupechestvo is a board game with historical elements. You will embark on a journey to medieval Russia during the period of the unification of the Russian lands and the heyday of the Grand Duchy of Lithuania (13th - 16th centuries) and try on the role of a merchant striving for fame and wealth.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Interactive tutorial.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/aaaa102dff5ae2cfdb262e2d950f6579.poster.avif?t=1750256150\" width=248 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/aaaa102dff5ae2cfdb262e2d950f6579.webm?t=1750256150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/aaaa102dff5ae2cfdb262e2d950f6579.mp4?t=1750256150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> 6 Scenarios filled with historical events.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/cc31a563ffddea4ead0226ff4bc7d406.avif?t=1750256150\" width=420 height=70 /></span><br></li><li> Battle against AI.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/bdf1eddc0ea468f5fb9f975baa8f9322.avif?t=1750256150\" width=70 height=70 /></span><br></li><li> Multiplayer.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/937631061b0eda8a605a59dd50030dd5.avif?t=1750256150\" width=70 height=70 /></span><br></li><li> Replay value thanks to various resource combinations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/b1f12f58f467233f7342c4fe4cde5729.poster.avif?t=1750256150\" width=592 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/b1f12f58f467233f7342c4fe4cde5729.webm?t=1750256150\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581090/extras/b1f12f58f467233f7342c4fe4cde5729.mp4?t=1750256150\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br>The official digital version of the board game Kupechestvo.",
